1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:05,212
Finding a flatmate in Bangalore used to mean a Facebook group post and a prayer.

2
00:00:05,162 --> 00:00:11,150
360 Flatmates fixes that with a six-dimension lifestyle compatibility engine.

3
00:00:11,150 --> 00:00:14,812
It is a Vite and React nineteen single-page app.

4
00:00:14,812 --> 00:00:23,675
TypeScript strict, Tailwind four with CSS custom property tokens, Zustand for client state, TanStack Query for server state.

5
00:00:23,675 --> 00:00:27,187
The product differentiator is compatibility.

6
00:00:27,187 --> 00:00:35,775
Six lifestyle dimensions: sleep schedule, cleanliness, food habits, smoking and drinking, guests policy, and work style.

7
00:00:35,775 --> 00:00:40,962
Each peer is scored per dimension, weighted, and summed into one percentage.

8
00:00:40,962 --> 00:00:44,150
Three surfaces sit on top of that engine.

9
00:00:44,150 --> 00:00:48,762
A public marketing surface with prerendered city and blog pages.

10
00:00:48,762 --> 00:00:54,612
An authenticated app with a swipe deck, likes, matches, chat, and visits.

11
00:00:54,612 --> 00:00:57,325
And an admin moderation queue.

12
00:00:57,325 --> 00:01:00,562
The swipe deck is the heart of the experience.

13
00:01:00,562 --> 00:01:03,712
Drag, keyboard, or action bar.

14
00:01:03,712 --> 00:01:08,187
Every swipe is an optimistic mutation with rollback on error.

15
00:01:08,187 --> 00:01:13,825
Real-time runs over Supabase private Broadcast from the backend bootstrap config.

16
00:01:13,825 --> 00:01:20,087
One hook handles six event types, reconnect backoff, and cache catch-up after outages.

17
00:01:20,087 --> 00:01:22,512
Auth goes through Supabase.

18
00:01:22,512 --> 00:01:26,425
Phone OTP, password, Google, and Apple.

19
00:01:26,425 --> 00:01:32,450
A gate-state guard enforces profile completion and onboarding before the user reaches the app.

20
00:01:32,450 --> 00:01:35,175
The build pipeline is unusual.

21
00:01:35,175 --> 00:01:41,675
After Vite builds the bundle, Playwright Chromium renders every public route to static HTML.

22
00:01:41,675 --> 00:01:46,987
This makes the SPA crawlable by LLM bots that do not run JavaScript.

23
00:01:46,987 --> 00:01:50,087
The design system is warm-editorial.

24
00:01:50,087 --> 00:01:57,250
Terracotta accent, Fraunces headlines, Inter body, a categorical palette with accessible ink tiers.

25
00:01:57,250 --> 00:02:03,337
Dark mode is first-class, applied via a data-theme attribute on the HTML element.

26
00:02:03,337 --> 00:02:08,837
Twenty-three commits, one contributor, thirty-eight thousand lines of TypeScript.

27
00:02:08,837 --> 00:02:13,850
The compatibility engine survived a rogue-agent deletion and was restored.

28
00:02:13,850 --> 00:02:16,662
Zero TODO comments in the source.

29
00:02:16,662 --> 00:02:19,375
360 Flatmates.

30
00:02:19,375 --> 00:02:22,375
Find your flatmate, not a nightmare.

